%N A010872 a(n) = n mod 3.
%C A010872 Fixed point of morphism 0 -> 01, 1 -> 20, 2 -> 12.
%C A010872 Complement of A002264, since 3*A002264(n) + a(n) = n. - _Hieronymus Fischer_, Jun 01 2007
